\begin_inset Formula $\left[1-r,1-l\right]$
\end_inset

 which we abbreviate 
\begin_inset Formula $1\tensor*[_{\mathscr{I}}]{-}{}\left[l,r\right]$
\end_inset

, where the preposing 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{I}$
\end_inset

